01:22:00.620 --> 01:22:04.920
<i>I don't want a pregnant woman to come
and say goodbye to me...</i>

01:22:05.120 --> 01:22:06.920
<i>because I don't approve it.</i>

01:22:08.020 --> 01:22:09.020
<i>Four....</i>

01:22:12.520 --> 01:22:15.420
<i>Some trust-fund prosecutor
got off message at Yale...</i>

01:22:15.620 --> 01:22:17.720
<i>thinks he's gonna run this
up the flagpole?</i>

01:22:17.920 --> 01:22:19.220
<i>Make a name for himself?</i>

01:22:19.420 --> 01:22:22.320
<i>Maybe get elected some two-bit
congressman from nowhere...</i>

01:22:22.420 --> 01:22:24.520
<i>with the result that China or Russia...</i>

01:22:24.620 --> 01:22:26.820
<i>can suddenly start having,
at our expense...</i>

01:22:26.920 --> 01:22:28.720
<i>all the advantages we enjoy here?</i>

01:22:29.120 --> 01:22:31.320
No, I tell you. No, sir.

