01:32:09.620 --> 01:32:13.920
He is barely qualified to run a brothel,
much less a country.

01:32:17.020 --> 01:32:19.320
I like Europe.

01:32:20.520 --> 01:32:23.220
I will be happy to stay here.

01:32:25.720 --> 01:32:27.820
