Everything seems fine.

01:36:40.320 --> 01:36:41.820
<i>How are we doing, Mr. Whiting?</i>

01:36:41.920 --> 01:36:43.920
Everything's fine.

01:36:57.920 --> 01:37:00.720
<i>- The door's unlocked.
- Did you leave it unlocked?</i>

