You're a good man.

01:37:55.020 --> 01:37:59.820
One whose experience
is narrow and deep.

01:38:00.020 --> 01:38:02.120
Your entire career...

01:38:02.320 --> 01:38:04.120
you've been used.

01:38:04.920 --> 01:38:08.820
